---
alwaysApply: true
---

🚧 Cursor Rule: Models MUST use Freezed
🔒 Mandatory Rule
All models MUST be created using:
freezed
json_serializable
📁 Where to Use Freezed
1. Data Layer Models (DTOs)

Location:

lib/src/data/models/
✅ Requirements:
Must use @freezed
Must include:
.freezed.dart
.g.dart

Must support JSON:

factory Model.fromJson(Map<String, dynamic> json) => _$ModelFromJson(json);
✅ Example:
@freezed
class UserProfileModel with _$UserProfileModel {
  const factory UserProfileModel({
    required String id,
    required String email,
    String? name,
  }) = _UserProfileModel;

  factory UserProfileModel.fromJson(Map<String, dynamic> json)
      => _$UserProfileModelFromJson(json);
}
2. Domain Entities (Optional but Recommended)

Location:

lib/src/domain/entities/
Rules:
Use Freezed only if:
You need immutability
You need unions/sealed classes
❌ No JSON in domain layer
3. Bloc (MANDATORY Freezed)
Events:
<feature>_event.dart
States:
<feature>_state.dart
Rules:
MUST use Freezed unions
No manual classes allowed
✅ Example:
@freezed
class LoginEvent with _$LoginEvent {
  const factory LoginEvent.loginRequested({
    required String email,
    required String password,
  }) = _LoginRequested;
}
@freezed
class LoginState with _$LoginState {
  const factory LoginState.initial() = _Initial;
  const factory LoginState.loading() = _Loading;
  const factory LoginState.success() = _Success;
  const factory LoginState.failure(String message) = _Failure;
}
🔥 Strict Enforcement Rules
❌ No plain Dart classes for models
❌ No mutable fields
❌ No manual copyWith
❌ No Equatable (Freezed replaces it)
❌ No JSON logic outside data models
⚙️ Required Setup

Make sure these are in pubspec.yaml:

dependencies:
  freezed_annotation: ^3.1.0
  json_annotation: ^4.9.0

dev_dependencies:
  build_runner: ^2.4.15
  freezed: ^3.1.0
  json_serializable: ^6.9.5
▶️ Code Generation Command
dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs
🧠 Extra Best Practices
Always add const constructors
Prefer required fields
Use @Default() for defaults
Use unions for:
API responses
Bloc states/events
✅ Final Combined Rule (Short Version for Cursor)

When creating any model, state, or event:

MUST use Freezed
MUST generate .freezed.dart and .g.dart
MUST keep JSON only in data layer
MUST keep immutability
